                         ] ;
         rdfs:comment "The step identifier as defined in the test program or schedule file. Values are instrument-defined and are not required to be contiguous or monotonically increasing; the same step ID may recur in successive cycles. Known equivalents: Arbin Step_Index, Neware Step_ID, Digatron Step, BioLogic Ns."@en ;
